data.meta_description: At Salesian College Preparatory, students have opportunities to develop academically, socially, and spiritually in a faith-based environment. Apply today!
data.text:
#WeAreSalesian

Salesian is a vibrant community and the PRIDE is always up to something academically, athletically or in service to the community. Get a glimpse into our world by clicking on Our News or via our recent posts using our official hashtag #WeAreSalesian on Instagram. If you like what you see, follow us!
